data.description: Don’t miss out on this fully renovated gem! Sitting on a large fully fenced lot, this 4 bed 2.5 bath home is sure to impress with beautiful LVP flooring, solid surface counters, updated kitchen, double vanity in both bathrooms, new windows and blinds, epoxy flooring in the garage and so much more! Conveniently located close to grocery stores, schools, parks, the green belt and in an HOA FREE subdivision, this home is the perfect fit for you! See furniture you like in the home? Make us an offer! Furniture is negotiable.
